Subject: Win11 can't install/uninstall/repair DLP 5.9,new version 6.3 can't be installed neither.
Description: Error MSG: Could not write value PlugPlayServiceType to keySystemCurrentControlSetServicesEndpoint Protector.Verify that you have suffident access tothat key,or contact your support personnel.
What_We_Know__c:
During the remote session I took control and used the ZAP tool to removed any remnants of the old appliance of EPP then deleted the achive + the extracted folder with SHIFT +Delete buttons.

After that we restarted the machine and tried to install a new version of EPP, and client was able to do it without a problem.
